
This directory provides the Top estimation based on exisiting smurf ntuples. 

1. To run the estimation, do 
make top

2. The output of this code is the data/MC scale factors to be used in the full analysis

TopBkgScaleFactors.h

3. To use this new scale factors, you need to replace the file in this directory

Smurf/Analysis/HWWlvlv/